wiki.summary: The Brazilian heathen-overlords Mystifier eminently return with their second overwhelming evil force. The music is a splice of early '90's black and death with centered occult influenced lyrics/song titles .From the previous output to here the production has more of an organic sound by comparison to how the production was processed on the first, and newest member Asmodeus's vocals are a further profane take on what Mystifier wanted to accomplish in extreme metal at this point. Read more on Last.fm.
